{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all these things, step by step, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he has this 1,000-page book of all these laws and regulations, chronologically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "With German help, he put this book together-- this man from Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kempner wrote the forward to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the foreword, the first paragraph of the forward-- unfortunately, I don't know it by heart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It includes how the Jews were treated in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The rest of the book has no text.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It has only this research on the regulations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the foreword of several pages was written by Robert Kempner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the first paragraph of that foreword was excerpted to make a monument that has been put up in the section of Berlin where Dr.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Kempner grew up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Kempner-- a quotation of Robert Kempner, taken from that book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Jew was-- I don't know-- all the step by step things, maybe five or six lines, on stone, engraved on stone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the names-- I'm not sure-- was it over 1,700 Jews of that area who were extradited or taken out of Berlin, of that section of Berlin where he grew up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't think his name is on it, except under this quotation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I haven't seen it, myself, but it's been publicized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's a great big monument in stone, black stone, enormous monument, with all the names of all the residents and their addresses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know whether it's the date of birth or the date of death of the people of that area.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what do you think, all those addresses?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How the people at those addresses like that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there was a lot of protest until the Berlin building minister put that up-- you know, it's an interesting monument.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The canary vogel is in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The canary bird.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
